## 📈 데이터 구조

### 코드 인덱스 테이블
```sql
CREATE TABLE code_index (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
  path TEXT UNIQUE,
  file_name TEXT,
  extension TEXT,
  functions TEXT,     -- JSON
  classes TEXT,       -- JSON
  content TEXT,
  lines_count INTEGER,
  quality_stars INTEGER,
  quality_category TEXT,
  last_modified TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);
```

### 검색 히스토리
```sql
CREATE TABLE search_history (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
  query TEXT,
  results_count INTEGER,
  search_time INTEGER,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);
```

### 캐시
```sql
CREATE TABLE cache (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
  key TEXT UNIQUE,
  value TEXT,
  expires_at TIMESTAMP,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);
```

